{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104580/extras/BG_600.png?t=1737140468\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow Azura, a curious and nature-loving adventurer, as she uncovers the secrets of the mysterious Vesperians, and their connection to the Primalis Crystals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore various landscapes, meet creatures and solve puzzles, and make choices that will shape your destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story-Driven Exploration: Uncover ancient lore and unravel the mystery of the Primalis as Azura continues on her journey</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dynamic Combat: Defeat enemies using a combination of elemental crystal powers. Summon mighty Vesperians to aid in battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crafting &amp; Resource Management: Gather resources from your surroundings, and craft tools, potions, and upgrades to aid you in your journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzle-Solving: Test your wit with environmental puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stunning Environments: Explore a variety of landscapes, from serene forests to treacherous caves and ruins, each environment is flush with its own unique flora and fauna</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vesperians: Harness the power of the mighty Vesperians that can help you in combat, research, and exploration. Each Vesperian offers unique abilities that can be upgraded over time.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737140468","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104580/page.bg.jpg?t=1737140468","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104580/f9ee59d35ac602b2173b6c03604ca6b